name: TheCryingBaby
0:
”Alexa, start the Crying Baby”
”Alexa, ask the Crying Baby for a random cry”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: the crying baby
des:
Please help... The Crying Baby just cannot stop making annoying crying sounds!

Just ask her to perform some of her best cries for you and who knows, that might make her happy!

Her selection of very fine cries include the...
 ...Normal cry
 ...Tired cry
 ...Angry cry 
 ...Bored cry
 ...'I want a cuddle' cry 
 ...Sleepy cry
 ...Starving cry
 ...'Wait For It' cry
 ...Grumpy cry
 ...'Mega Tantrum' cry (not for the faint-hearted!)

Can't decide? Just ask for a random cry and the expert will choose for you!

Enjoy!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
